{"id": "1263212812721721444", "channel_id": "1255628728659087641", "type": 0, "author_id": "422799061133950978", "author_name": "ernest_heart", "author_bot": false, "content": "```　　莎莉娜總是帶著一副黑色的皮手套，也可能不是皮做的，不管在任何光照下它都不會有任何的反光。或許是因為如此，她的雙手顯現出驚人的雪白，讓人看著看著就出了神。\n　　但要小心，要是太入神的話，可是會忽略時間流逝的。木桌在她的優雅中敗朽，鐵門在她的美麗中鏽壞，就連翩翩飛舞到她手中的蝴蝶，都為之化為齏粉。```\n角色立繪：[AI製圖](https://www.pinterest.com/pin/5981411999072333/)\n命輪圖示：[宇宙](https://www.flaticon.com/free-icon/astronomy_5005763?term=universe&page=1&position=19&origin=tag&related_id=5005763)", "timestamp": "2024-07-17T19:16:43.912000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🥺", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1263212812797214853", "filename": "4937bdbc21097a42.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 21197, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255628728659087641/1263212812797214853/4937bdbc21097a42.jpg?ex=69cc1d9b&is=69cacc1b&hm=8c14cc0e57f0461d23bf480e34ea0a5377f2115fd9b88548e666e9898adefddd&"}, {"id": "1263212813044945007", "filename": "1.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 131501, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255628728659087641/1263212813044945007/1.jpg?ex=69cc1d9b&is=69cacc1b&hm=c9955fc2c345931b2f310c7186d9a62dfea6f3dca7befac1715557683fec60f2&"}, {"id": "1263212813313118208", "filename": "1.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 127639, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255628728659087641/1263212813313118208/1.jpg?ex=69cc1d9c&is=69cacc1c&hm=6c30a50e7b9bcfaf85ed7d89738dac59a33cf3255f10c6cae30a2ff625f93662&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255628728659087641", "flags": 4, "thread_title": "自創界域投稿：謬妄Absurdity", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359914895646811"]}
{"id": "1263214474307833947", "channel_id": "1255628728659087641", "type": 0, "author_id": "422799061133950978", "author_name": "ernest_heart", "author_bot": false, "content": "```　　來自東方的神祕與詭麗，何馨總是江面龐遮掩在寫著扭曲字符的摺扇之下，引起不少學生的好奇。為此彌薩格大學不得不訂下規定，禁止學生們接近這位高貴的客人，任何的會面都必須透過通訊器間接對話。這也是個好主意，畢竟在她香甜濃粉之外，總有股令人反胃的無味氣息。```\n角色立繪：[COC戰役封面](https://inkvoltage.com/call-of-cthulhu-rpg-mask-of-nyarlathotep-illustrations)\n命輪圖示：[女人](https://www.flaticon.com/free-icon/avatar_7030138?term=woman&related_id=7030138)、[骷髏](https://www.flaticon.com/free-icon/skull_9352699?term=dead+body&page=1&position=13&origin=tag&related_id=9352699)、[摺扇](https://www.flaticon.com/free-icon/fan-paper_12291150?term=folding+fan&page=1&position=3&origin=search&related_id=12291150)", "timestamp": "2024-07-17T19:23:20.065000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1263214474538782753", "filename": "b816ecc4538c0028.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 20850, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255628728659087641/1263214474538782753/b816ecc4538c0028.jpg?ex=69cc1f28&is=69cacda8&hm=649fd799417639828be724536e4cd7318f94bea957541726ca3cc20fac2aa26c&"}, {"id": "1263214474916139048", "filename": "2.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 141679, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255628728659087641/1263214474916139048/2.jpg?ex=69cc1f28&is=69cacda8&hm=7d037ca923596e741f2f7b909df17172cbf69b761381abb7cfabc5bbddc6b39c&"}, {"id": "1263214475213799514", "filename": "2.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 150982, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255628728659087641/1263214475213799514/2.jpg?ex=69cc1f28&is=69cacda8&hm=8fd83f5e618594e5b9c4f8fa754177a2786368e426745d05c8b22da7a6a66ee4&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255628728659087641", "flags": 4, "thread_title": "自創界域投稿：謬妄Absurdity", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359914895646811"]}
